Weather application designed for collecting and storing temperature measurements from indicated locations  in given time interval.

Application gains access to API OpenWeatherMap with SSH key. 

User can pass city name and then location name and ID is being saved to database. 
App uses Quartz â€“ Job Scheduler library which triggers download temperature from location with indicated frequency (in sec. ) 
and add measurements to database

Request: 
[GET]/api/register/{city_name}/{frequency}
